that is always there.

179
00:10:00,602 --> 00:10:02,414
I need to talk to someone.

180
00:10:02,963 --> 00:10:05,536
I know a guy named Tom Collins.
He's a great listener.

181
00:10:06,038 --> 00:10:07,622
