the dirty things I'd do to him.

243
00:13:32,205 --> 00:13:33,810
- Like what?
- Oh, god!

244
00:13:33,869 --> 00:13:37,025
Oh! I didn't know you were...

245
00:13:38,753 --> 00:13:40,120
I'm Susan Delfino.

246
00:13:40,258 --> 00:13:41,106
Ah.

247
00:13:41,106 --> 00:13:42,100
